{"id":602267,"date":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":5}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"84","ytitle":"","mtitle":"荷花(外一首)","ftitle":"","authors":["龚咏燕"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"龚咏燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵漂浮水上的荷花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座翡翠的工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它从不浪费一寸光阴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累累果实就在脚下收藏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗橙黄的玉米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首秋天的诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它告诉了人们:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有汗，才有珠玑。"}]}